\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Ray diagram for experiment 1C (ii).
 Translating the mirror is equivalent to changing 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{0}$
\end_inset

, whereas rotating the mirror corresponds to a change in 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{0}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset


